quran[54]{c,v,t}:
  20,1,Twâ-Hâ
  20,2,Nganituntuluchisya mmwe (Muhammadi ﷺ) Qur’an kuti nnagasiche
  20,3,Nambo kuti jiŵe chikumbusyo kwa mundu jwaakun’jogopa (Allah)
  20,4,Chakutulusyidwa chakuumila kwa Ajula jwaŵagumbile litaka ni mawunde gagali kwinani nnope
  20,5,"(Jwalakwe ni Allah) Jwaukoto wejinji, jwatenjele pa Arishi (Chindanda Chaulungu katenjele kakulandana ni uchimbichimbi Ŵakwe)"
  20,6,"Iŵele Yakwe yosope yaili kumawunde ni yaili petaka ni yaili chilikati chakwe, kwika soni yaili pasi petaka"
  20,7,"Sano kanga chinnyanyiche liloŵe (pakuomba duwa kapena kutenda mwakusongona; yalumope), ngati chisimu Jwalakwe (Allah) jukumanyilila yaasili ni yakusisika nnope"
  20,8,"Allah! Pangali nnungu jwine (jwakuŵajilwa kun’galagatila) ikaŵeje Jwele pejo, Jwalakwe jukwete Mena gambone nnope"
  20,9,Soni ana jinyyiche abali ja Musa
  20,10,"Ndema jajwauweni moto, basi ni jwalisalile liŵasa lyakwe kuti: “Jembechelani! Chisimu une nauweni moto; mwine une kuŵa nkwika nacho kukwenu chisinga kuumila mu walakweo, kapena chingapate pa motopo jwakunondolela (litala).”"
  20,11,"Basi ndema jajwauŵichilile (motowo) jwaŵilanjidwe (kuti): “E mmwe Musa!”"
  20,12,“Chisimu Une ni Nam’mbuje gwenu! Basi wulani ilatu yenu; chisimutu mmwe n’di pachiŵata chakutakata (chakuŵilanjikwa) Tuwaa.”
  20,13,"“Soni Une nansagwile (kuŵa Ntume), basi pikanilani yaikujuwulidwa.”"
  20,14,"“Chisimu Une ni Allah! Pangali nnungu jwine (jwakuŵajilwa kun’galagatila) ikaŵeje Unepe, basi mungalagatilani, ni n’jimicheje Swala mwakolosya pakungumbuchila Une.”"
  20,15,"“Chisimu Kiyama jikwisa, melepe ngujisisa, kuti mundu jwalijose akalipidwe pa yaakupanganya.”"
  20,16,"“Sano akasansiŵilikanganya ata panandi kuleka (kulupilila) ya jalakwejo ajula jwangakujikulupilila, ni jugamba kuya isako yakwe; ntakwisa mwan’jonasiche.”"
  20,17,“Ana nichichi chele chachili mu nkono wenu wan’dyo mmwe Musa?”
  20,18,"Jwalakwe jwatite: “Jalakweji nisimbo jangu, ngujijegamilaga jalakweji (pakwenda), ni ngupakatichisyaga masamba gakulichisya ngondolo syangu, nambo soni une ngwete mu jalakweji ipaka ine.”"
  20,19,"(Allah) jwatite: “Jiponyani mmwe Musa!”"
  20,20,Ni ŵajiponyisye; basi ajile sai ŵajiweni jisyuchile lijoka lyakwenda mwaluŵilo
  20,21,"(Allah) jwatite: “Likamulani, soni nkajogopa. Chituliuchisye mu kaŵe kakwe kandanda (kuŵa simbo).”"
  20,22,"“Soni kwapatisyani ligasa lyenu kungwapa kwenu; chilikopoche lili lyeswela (lyakumelemenda) ngaŵaga mwaulwele, (chele nikuŵa) chisimosimo chine.”"
  20,23,“Kuti tunnosye ine mu isimosimo Yetu yekulungwakulungwa.”
  20,24,"“Jaawulani kwa Firiauna, chisimu jwalakwejo jusumbile mpika (pakulikwesya).”"
  20,25,"(Musa) jwatite: “Ambuje ŵangu! Sapangulilani chidali changu.”"
  20,26,“Nimunjepepachisye masengo gangu.”
  20,27,“Soni gopolaani chiundo palulimi pangu (ngaŵechetaga mwachimeme).”
  20,28,“Kuti (ŵandu) akapikanichisyeje yakuŵecheta yangu.”
  20,29,“Soni mbichilaani nkungamuchisya jwakuumila kwiŵasa kwangu.”
  20,30,"“(Jwali) Haruna, nkulugwangu.”"
  20,31,“Limbisyani ni jwalakwejo machili gangu.”
  20,32,“Soni mum’bwangani mmasengo gangu (gakulungusya utenga).”
  20,33,“Kuti tunswejesyeje Mmwejo (Allah) kwejinji.”
  20,34,“Ni tunkumbuchileje kwejinji.”
  20,35,“Chisimu Mmwe m’bele ŵakutulolechesya uwwe.”
  20,36,"(Allah) jwatite: “Pamasile pampedwile iŵendo yenuyo, E mmwe Musa!”"
  20,37,“Soni chisimu chene Uwwe twampele mmwe ukoto ndaŵi jine (kalakala).”
  20,38,“Ndema jatwajuwulile mama ŵenu yatwajuwulile.”
  20,39,"“(Yanti) mum’biikaani jwalakwe (mwanachejo) mwibokosi, ni nkaliŵiche nnusulo, basi lusulo chilumponye munjengwe, (sano palakwepo) amagongo Ŵangu ŵali soni amagongo ŵakwe tan’jigale. Ni naŵisile chinonyelo penumwe chakuuma Kukwangu (kuti m’be ŵakunonyeledwa ni ŵandu wosope), nambo soni kuti nneledwe kwa Liso Lyangu (mwakuloledwa ni Une).”"
  20,40,"“(Kumbuchilani) katema kaŵajendaga alumbu ŵenu (kuja kwiŵasa lya Firiauna) ni kuja kuti: ‘Ana nannanjile kwa mundu jwampaka akombole kunnela jwalakweju?’ Basi ni twam’buchisye kwa achikulu ŵenu, kuti gatulale meso gao, nambo soni kuti akadandaula. Kaneka ni mwauleje mundu (mwakuluchisya), basi ni twan’jokwele ku madandausi gamakulungwa, ni twan’dinjile mmwejo ni mayeso gausito nnope. Kaneka mwatemi yaka igala ni ŵandu ŵa ku Madyana. Kaneko nim’biche (apa) mwampango (Ŵangu wakumpa utume n’di niyaka makumi ncheche) E mmwe Musa!”"
  20,41,“Ni nansagwile mmwejo kulisagulila Nansyene (kuti m’be ntume Jwangu).”
  20,42,"“Jaulani mmwe ni akuluŵenu pamo ni isimosimo Yangu, soni ngasimpela pakungumbuchila Une.”"
  20,43,"“Jaawulani ŵanaŵaŵilimmwe kwa Firiauna, chisimu jwalakwejo jusumbile mpika (pakulikwesya).”"
  20,44,“Basi ni nkansalile maloŵe gakoloŵa kuti mwine jwalakwejo chijukachetelele kapena chijukajogope.”
  20,45,"Ŵanganyao ŵatite: “Ambuje ŵetu! Chisimu uwwe tukogopa kuti chakatuguŵatile (nkanituyiche mwakuŵecheta chilichose) kapena chakasumbe mpika (wakutulagachisya ni kulikwesya).”"
  20,46,"(Allah) jwatite: “Nkajogopa, chisimu Une ndinamwe, ngupikana soni ngulola.”"
  20,47,"“Basi mun’jaulilani, ni nkajile: ‘Chisimu uwwe mitenga jiŵili ja Ambuje ŵenu, basi mwalekani aŵigule nowe ŵanache ŵa Israila, soni ngasimwalagasya. Chisimu tum’bichilile ni chisimosimo chakuumila kwa Ambuje ŵenu. Sano ntendele chiuŵe kwa mundu jwaakukuya chongoko.’"
  20,48,"‘Chisimu uwwe ijuwulidwe kukwetu yanti: Chisimu ilagasyo chiiŵe kwa mundu jwaakukanila (yalakweyi) ni galauchila kumbali.”"
  20,49,"(Firiauna) jwatite: “Ana M’mbuje gwenujo ninduni, E mmwe Musa?”"
  20,50,"(Musa) jwatite: “M’mbuje gwetu ni Ajula jwaachipele chindu chilichose kagumbidwe kakwe, kaneka ni kuchijongolela (ku yaachiguumbiile).”"
  20,51,"(Firiauna) jwatite: “Nambi mikutula jandanda jili uli (jajapite mmwe nkanim’biche)?”"
  20,52,"(Musa) jwatite: “Umanyilisi waajimanya jalakwejo uli kwa Ambuje ŵangu m’chitabu (chailembedwemo ichindu yosope), Ambuje ŵangu ŵangaŵa nkusoya namuno kuliŵalila.”"
  20,53,"Ajula jwam’biichiile litaka kuŵa chakutandika, ni ampaanjiile mwalakwemo matala, ni atulwisye kuumila kwinani mesi (gawula), ni tukopwesye ni galakwego mitundu jakulekanganalekangana ja mmela"
  20,54,Lyagani soni illichisyeje ilango yenu. Chisimu mu yalakweyo mwana ilosyo kwa achinsyene lunda